- Fixes the unterminated `TEMPLATE` string (proper open/close `"""`).
- Completes the HTML/Jinja2 block (no truncation).
- Restricts `/file` serving to only paths under your defined `ROOTS` (so you don’t accidentally expose arbitrary files).
- Adds `preload="metadata"` for videos/audio for lighter load.
- Keeps your summaries, sorting toggles, and lazy loading intact.

